  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/5112884596acdfb50e08b7a359a78324.avif?t=1737129867\" width=616 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/6aad91f0cc7a07e88a140127a4293013.avif?t=1737129867\" width=616 height=75 /></span><strong>Overnight Watch</strong> is a game where the supernatural meets surveillance! In this game, you step into the shoes of a fresh recruit at Paranormal Security, a cutting-edge company tasked with monitoring live surveillance cameras to detect and fix any unearthly anomalies that may arise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a new employee, you'll find yourself stationed in the heart of the company's monitoring center, equipped with various surveillance equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your primary objective? Keep a keen eye on the live feeds from various locations and be vigilant for any signs of paranormal activity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware, the paranormal entities won't make it easy for you. They'll manifest in various forms and it's up to you to quickly identify and report these anomalies before they escalate. Who knows, <strong>maybe they're closer to you than you think...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/b7ee24eb7560c1ddb79bd71ea8727106.avif?t=1737129867\" width=616 height=75 /></span>Report anomalies by clicking and with the submenu</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/93398a73bf4a8a5e77b3746ad7361610.poster.avif?t=1737129867\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/93398a73bf4a8a5e77b3746ad7361610.webm?t=1737129867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/93398a73bf4a8a5e77b3746ad7361610.mp4?t=1737129867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/0afbbd58afaa32aef894a044a0493a90.avif?t=1737129867\" width=616 height=75 /></span><strong>Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unreal Engine Dynamic Lighting - Lumen </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cloud Saving & Steam Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14 different anomaly types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 total anomalies on the first map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Difficulties modes & Custom difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > More in the works </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Are you ready to uncover the truth lurking in the shadows? Join Paranormal Security and embark on a spine-tingling adventure like no other!</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/5112884596acdfb50e08b7a359a78324.avif?t=1737129867\" width=616 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/6aad91f0cc7a07e88a140127a4293013.avif?t=1737129867\" width=616 height=75 /></span><strong>Overnight Watch</strong> is a game where the supernatural meets surveillance! In this game, you step into the shoes of a fresh recruit at Paranormal Security, a cutting-edge company tasked with monitoring live surveillance cameras to detect and fix any unearthly anomalies that may arise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a new employee, you'll find yourself stationed in the heart of the company's monitoring center, equipped with various surveillance equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your primary objective? Keep a keen eye on the live feeds from various locations and be vigilant for any signs of paranormal activity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware, the paranormal entities won't make it easy for you. They'll manifest in various forms and it's up to you to quickly identify and report these anomalies before they escalate. Who knows, <strong>maybe they're closer to you than you think...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/b7ee24eb7560c1ddb79bd71ea8727106.avif?t=1737129867\" width=616 height=75 /></span>Report anomalies by clicking and with the submenu</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/93398a73bf4a8a5e77b3746ad7361610.poster.avif?t=1737129867\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/93398a73bf4a8a5e77b3746ad7361610.webm?t=1737129867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/93398a73bf4a8a5e77b3746ad7361610.mp4?t=1737129867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940030/extras/0afbbd58afaa32aef894a044a0493a90.avif?t=1737129867\" width=616 height=75 /></span><strong>Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unreal Engine Dynamic Lighting - Lumen </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cloud Saving & Steam Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14 different anomaly types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 total anomalies on the first map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Difficulties modes & Custom difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > More in the works </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Are you ready to uncover the truth lurking in the shadows? Join Paranormal Security and embark on a spine-tingling adventure like no other!</h2>",
